Siskiyou County Sheriffs Office has issued an EVACUATION WARNING for Zones SIS-1712, 1713 & 1811 due to the Butler Fire.... Anyone in this area should be prepared to leave.... For the latest information regarding this or any other emergency impacting Siskiyou County go to the ReadySiskiyou Website at www.readysiskiyou.gov

FIRE HAS REACHED KNOWNOTHING CREEK ROAD

IF YOU ARE WEST OF KNOWNOTHING CREEK ROAD, PLEASE DRIVE UP TO FORKS OF SALMON AND EVACUATE WITH THE GROUP GOING BACK UP SAYWERS BAR ROAD AWAY FROM THE FIRE. 

IF YOU ARE EAST OF KNOWNOTHING CREEK, PLEASE USE CECILVILLE/CALLAHAN RD TO EVACUATE.
